<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_bff47d6f-8c3c-4ab7-83bc-5ec48a47cc1a" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>E4V1</sptc><title id="_09c2f5fa-2246-4324-93d6-1c3184a265a4">Emergency lighting</title><archive-num>2019: EV4.1</archive-num><subclause id="_7a98abaa-fe5b-4f34-abb0-91ab0b6b17cd" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_fbfd5f03-f877-4856-a17a-c0d0c080b597">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Compliance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2813_2.2.0.xml#_06fe7c1e-7d97-4b0e-b533-1803b79fec76" id="_09afa4e3-94c8-4518-9eeb-3ea4edbebdaf" scope="local" type="clause">E4P1</xref> is verified for the level of visibility for safe evacuation in an emergency and instantaneous activation, when an emergency lighting system satisfies the requirements of (2) to (5).</p></subclause><subclause id="_cd2d99c0-80a3-4515-9c2f-f71ddb16bb84" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8d1e8313-fc2f-4f28-9dad-4d989c8085d3">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The calculated horizontal <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1346_0.5.0.xml#_f3fc0ea9-6656-4e98-b020-380b3ab68684" id="_afe5a4c0-0d5c-4a6a-87aa-379e5980b86f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">illuminance</xref> is not less than—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_bb1f9fc5-af1a-4883-8266-ac79d6f1a36c">0.2 lux at floor level in the path of travel to an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_f1caed7b-7311-413a-8635-23307d270686" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref>; and</li><li id="_e97d185a-5fe4-46c8-89e1-9fbf4bf4784c">1 lux at each floor level or tread in every <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_ef6efce1-cebb-49fc-976f-54ec85d936d5" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref>—<ol><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1285_2.1.0.xml#_c71e675e-d6e1-4612-8e59-381a56e224a8" id="_1aa2283d-7a5e-439f-9e08-a41b4158e992" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated stairway</xref>; or</li><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1283_2.0.0.xml#_2f0af1de-a7c1-44b9-a8b5-1faaedfdb023" id="_d7675cd5-10b6-4e05-a33b-6dd57fdc2fc8" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated passageway</xref>; or</li><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1284_2.0.0.xml#_cfa6cc89-aa6c-4eaf-90e6-8aabe04b9c76" id="_a732a98a-cc18-4018-9aef-496fb283c6cf" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated ramp</xref>; or</li><li>non-<xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1285_2.1.0.xml#_c71e675e-d6e1-4612-8e59-381a56e224a8" id="_408b0aef-edd7-476b-8932-2752ffecb7e7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated stairway</xref>; or</li><li>non-<xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1284_2.0.0.xml#_cfa6cc89-aa6c-4eaf-90e6-8aabe04b9c76" id="_bfb6a757-99e6-471c-9fdd-32a2dc827729" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated ramp</xref>.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_62f0e92b-d322-4885-bb8b-262e465945ab" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_795e9642-7150-41f4-9223-5df9ef4b386f">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>The emergency lighting provides a level of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1346_0.5.0.xml#_f3fc0ea9-6656-4e98-b020-380b3ab68684" id="_dc770d0d-aa9c-4bb8-989c-919a38b4dc06" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">illuminance</xref> not less than—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_00a40bca-bb03-4dbf-aec8-ba16fc31d92b">10% of that <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_eb97addc-a245-481e-a681-5d8cb403f89e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (2) within 1 second of energisation; and</li><li id="_4271fdcf-77d1-47e9-9f28-c204ce229343">80% of that <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_c8e57d14-8285-49d8-9e0e-ee7784a4e6bf" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (2) within 15 seconds of energisation.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_dc9077cf-a464-49e6-a49d-7cd088ae24a9" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_697314d8-a4c1-43d1-a290-c137571b4fc3">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>The full level of illumination <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_c4fcf689-dc1d-4eae-a290-0ab4716d1aaa" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (2) must be achieved within 60 seconds of energisation.</p></subclause><subclause id="_f5dbff81-4006-49eb-9373-6b367041b7aa" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ac482dbd-8c35-44f1-97b5-5df8490fa582">SubClause</title><num>5</num><p>An emergency lighting system must operate at not less than the minimum <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_a196151f-e868-4b2f-badb-821213ef0ffe" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> level of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1346_0.5.0.xml#_f3fc0ea9-6656-4e98-b020-380b3ab68684" id="_40a8acf2-d2a3-4030-aed5-d48dc9a474da" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">illuminance</xref> for not less than 90 minutes.</p></subclause></clause>